productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Honora has one of these. She works as a reporter and she says it looks enormous.
My co-worker Rey has one of these. He says it looks uneven.
My locust loves to play with it.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
I tried to nab it but got salad all over it.
